query_save_inhibit
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
query_save_inhibit

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
query_save_inhibit -  This method returns the value of the disallowing save variable.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int query_save_inhibit()
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/global/player.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method returns the value of the disallowing save variable.  If this
is a non-zero value then the player must not be saved.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
allow_save(), disallow_save()

.EP

